org.wattdepot.common.domainmodel

Class MeasurementPruningDefinition

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.wattdepot.common.domainmodel.MeasurementPruningDefinition
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IDomainModel

    public class MeasurementPruningDefinition
extends Object
implements IDomainModel
    MeasurementPruningDefinition - Represents the information about a process that down samples the measurements for a particular Depository and Sensor. The process ensures that there is a minimum gap between measurements.
    Author:
    Cam Moore

        public MeasurementPruningDefinition(String name,
                            String depositoryId,
                            String sensorId,
                            String orgId,
                            Integer ignore,
                            Integer collect,
                            Integer gap)
        Parameters:
        name - The name of the garbage collection definition.
        depositoryId - The id of the depository.
        sensorId - The id of the sensor.
        orgId - The id of the organization.
        ignore - The number of days to ignore starting from now.
        collect - The number of days to garbage collect in.
        gap - The minimum gap between measurements in seconds.
